  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "How is the placement at IIHMR Jaipur?",
  "response": "IIHMR University Jaipur (formerly known as IIHMR Delhi) is renowned for its specialized programs in hospitality, tourism, and healthcare management. The placement scenario at IIHMR Jaipur is generally strong, reflecting the institution's focus on providing industry-relevant education and fostering strong ties with leading organizations. Here's an overview of the placement landscape at IIHMR Jaipur:\n\n### **1. Placement Statistics**\n- **Placement Percentage:** IIHMR Jaipur boasts a high placement rate, with over **90-95%** of graduating students securing placements annually. This rate can vary slightly depending on the program and economic conditions.\n- **Average Salary Package:** The average salary packages range between **INR 4-8 lakhs per annum**, with some specialized roles offering higher compensation. Top performers and those recruited by multinational companies may receive higher packages.\n- **Highest Salary Packages:** Some students secure packages upwards of **INR 15 lakhs per annum**, especially those placed in senior management roles or international firms.\n\n### **2. Top Recruiting Companies**\nIIHMR Jaipur attracts a diverse range of companies from various sectors, particularly in hospitality, tourism, healthcare, and management consulting. Some of the prominent recruiters include:\n- **Healthcare Sector:** Fortis Healthcare, Apollo Hospitals, Manipal Hospitals, Johnson & Johnson, and Medanta.\n- **Hospitality & Tourism:** Marriott International, Taj Hotels, Hilton, Oberoi Hotels, and AccorHotels.\n- **Management Consulting:** McKinsey & Company, Deloitte, KPMG, Ernst & Young, and PwC.\n- **Others:** Amazon, Flipkart, Dassault Systemes, and IndiGo Airlines.\n\n### **3. Internship Opportunities**\n- **Structured Internship Programs:** IIHMR Jaipur emphasizes practical experience through mandatory internships that are integrated into the curriculum. Students undergo internships in reputable organizations, which often lead to full-time job offers.\n- **Corporate Partnerships:** The institution has strong ties with industry leaders, facilitating numerous internship placements each year.\n\n### **4. Skill Development and Training**\n- **Training Programs:** The Placement Cell conducts regular training sessions, workshops, and soft skills development programs to prepare students for the corporate environment.\n- **Mock Interviews and Seminars:** Students participate in mock interviews, group discussions, and industry seminars to enhance their employability.\n- **Resume Building and Counseling:** Personalized resume building, career counseling, and interview preparation are integral parts of the placement support provided.\n\n### **5. Alumni Network**\n- **Strong Alumni Presence:** IIHMR Jaipur has a vast and active alumni network spread across various industries globally. This network assists in mentoring current students and providing valuable job leads and referrals.\n\n### **6. Special Programs and Certifications**\n- **Certifications:** The university offers various certification courses in project management, digital marketing, and other relevant fields, which add value to the students' profiles.\n- **Executive Education:** Specialized programs designed for working professionals help bridge the gap between academic learning and industry requirements.\n\n### **7. Placement Cell**\n- **Dedicated Team:** The Placement Cell at IIHMR Jaipur is dedicated to ensuring that students have access to the best opportunities. The team works proactively to connect students with potential employers.\n- **Regular Interactions:** Frequent interaction with companies through campus drives, guest lectures, and networking events keeps the students informed about the latest industry trends and job openings.\n\n### **8. Factors Contributing to Successful Placements**\n- **Industry-Relevant Curriculum:** The programs are designed to meet industry standards, ensuring that graduates possess the skills required by employers.\n- **Practical Exposure:** Case studies, live projects, and hands-on training prepare students for real-world challenges.\n- **Soft Skills Emphasis:** Focus on communication, leadership, and teamwork skills enhances overall employability.\n\n### **Conclusion**\nIIHMR University Jaipur provides a conducive environment for placements, backed by a robust curriculum, strong industry connections, and dedicated placement support. While the exact placement figures can fluctuate annually based on market conditions and other factors, the institution consistently performs well in placing its graduates in reputable organizations across various sectors.\n\nFor the most current and detailed placement statistics, including specific recruiters for a given year, it's recommended to visit the [official IIHMR Jaipur Placement page](https://iihrm.ac.in/) or contact their Placement Cell directly.",
